<p class="body-text">In Chicago's competitive plumbing market, brand recognition is everything. Homeowners searching for a plumber often choose the company they've seen in their neighborhood — not the first Google result. A fleet of wrapped vans creates the perception of a large, established, professional operation — whether you have 3 vans or 30.</p>
<p class="body-text">The economics are undeniable: at $0.04 CPM (cost per thousand impressions), plumbing fleet wraps deliver 90x more impressions per dollar than Google Ads ($3.56 CPM). A single $3,500 van wrap generates an estimated 16+ million impressions over its 5-year lifespan — the equivalent of $57,000+ in digital ad spend. With zero recurring cost and 100% tax deductibility, fleet wraps are the highest-ROI marketing investment for plumbing companies.</p>
